{"tid":772450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB男神？余德丞 西區踢波昏迷留醫ICU","createTime":"2018-08-08T18:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T01:20:08.000Z","uid":45148,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03a09a91ac8f2698175ca5a66ff3e6ee390023d8","tid":772450,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T18:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/020516_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F020516_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e2973c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女主持人？<br />\n<br />\n近期人氣急升，被稱為新一代男神的無綫電視藝員余德丞（Dickson），昨晚在西營盤中山紀念公園球場踢波，疑身體不適在場外一張長椅休息，其間突然暈倒昏迷送院，至凌晨仍在深切治療部搶救，大批親友在醫院等候，為他祈禱祝福。"},{"pid":"5f36bf8814e47a2c930f1aa912e4954a8b3eba8f","tid":772450,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T21:24:38.000Z","msg":"死咗未？"},{"pid":"5257753e40c0219076e63202a6e38443bafa91fb","tid":772450,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T23:27:23.000Z","msg":"警方經初步調查後相信事件沒可疑，列作有人暈倒案。十多名波友及親友知悉事件後，趕到醫院守候，各人顯得憂心忡忡。記者問及Dickson情況，其阿姨多謝關心，<span style=\"color: red;\">表哥</span>表示當時不在場，未知實際情況。至凌晨1時許，約6、7名親友離開醫院，未有回應記者提問。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/072716_ba34d077711090c27ddc73b1ccc43d13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F072716_ba34d077711090c27ddc73b1ccc43d13.png&h=b7f42c93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8202ad22a8cd14bc975c8d4b5d28032035904964","tid":772450,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T23:41:48.000Z","msg":"邊個黎？"},{"pid":"ed8ab495b83c7b156b8740efb1efbe566df6389f","tid":772450,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:18:13.000Z","msg":"渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b58846a817445150bf260e0654b6ae173eed45","tid":772450,"uid":147569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"【07:32】余德丞目前情況危殆<br />\n<br />\n有無醫學巴打解釋下救得番機會大唔大"}]}